items.sentence: Tom is the only person who volunteered to help me.
Everyone knew Tom didn't like living in Australia.
Do you think that Tom will stay in Australia long?
Do you think Tom wants to go to Australia with us?
Are you sure you want to go to Australia with Tom?
I didn't know Tom was planning to go to Australia.
I didn't know Tom would be in Australia this week.
I didn't think Tom would be in Australia all week.
I didn't know that Tom had relatives in Australia.
For some reason, Tom didn't want to talk about it.
